        "faq_items": [
            { "q": "How does the FoodHub platform work?", "a": "A QR code is created for your restaurant. Customers scan it, the online menu opens, and they can order. All orders are visible in the admin panel in real time, and a Telegram notification is sent." },
            { "q": "How long does it take to set up the menu?", "a": "After the demo request, the admin panel and menu page are ready within 24 hours. Adding dishes takes just a few minutes." },
            { "q": "How does the payment system work?", "a": "Available plans: monthly ($20), 6-month ($100) or yearly ($100 — special promotional price). Payment via Payme, Click or card." },
            { "q": "How are orders received?", "a": "Every order is instantly sent to the waiter or manager in Telegram. All orders are also visible in the admin panel in real time." },
            { "q": "Does multilingual menu work well?", "a": "Yes! The menu automatically works in Uzbek, Russian and English. Customers see the menu in their own language." },
            { "q": "Does it work without the internet?", "a": "The platform uses PWA (Progressive Web App) technology. The menu is cached, but the internet is needed to submit orders." },
            { "q": "How long is the demo period?", "a": "After submitting the form, a free 3-day demo is provided. During this time all features work fully." },
            { "q": "What support is available?", "a": "Technical support via Telegram and phone — 24/7. Answer to any question within 1 hour." }
        ]
